To install puppet on a fresh raspberry pi:

- ssh pi@raspberrypi
- sudo apt-get update
- sudo apt-get install puppet-common
- sudo apt-get install git
- sudo mv /etc/puppet ~
- cd /etc
- sudo git clone git://github.com/yorrick/puppet.git

To update raspberry pi:

- ssh yorrick@raspberrypi
- sudo git --git-dir=/etc/puppet/.git pull 
- sudo puppet apply /etc/puppet/manifests/config.pp 
